{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_BKiQHo6wnqz73aVXJXfLKS8w","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Spec Interview Complete for TST-001\n\n**Status:** Spec is **ready** with 2 blocker questions pending\n\n### Summary\n\nThe spec file `aidd/docs/spec/TST-001.spec.yaml` has been populated with:\n\n- **3 user flows**: admin role change, unauthorized access, live session update\n- **API contracts**: Mutation APIs enforcement, role change endpoint, WebSocket session sync\n- **Data model**: `audit_log` table schema with 8 fields\n- **Tradeoffs**: In-memory cache vs Redis, WebSocket vs polling\n- **Risks**: Performance impact, session desync, audit log growth, WebSocket instability\n- **Test strategy**: Unit, integration, contract, e2e with critical paths mapped to AC-1 through AC-4\n\n### Blocker Questions\n\nPlease answer the two questions above about:\n1. **Database schema** for existing users/roles tables\n2. **WebSocket infrastructure** availability\n\n### Next Step\n\nOnce blockers are resolved, run:\n```\n/feature-dev-aidd:tasks-new TST-001\n```\n\nThis will generate the tasklist from the spec and move to implementation planning."}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":33452,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":33452,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"47d41226-ac75-40b0-ac11-528554f314b7","uuid":"ed91d5f0-c55f-42f8-aae6-0ae4d0fea610"}
